    <span class="badge">Search</span>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white md:text-4xl">Find anything in seconds</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-300">
      Instantly filter through projects and writing. Powered by a static MiniSearch index that ships with the build,
